				<wikidot:authorName>Gene R</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>634139</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You may want to rethink</p> <blockquote> <p>dinosaur-based ectomorphs</p> </blockquote> <p>cause an ectomorph is a body type (the lean and wiry kind).</p> 
				 	]]>
