				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Okay, so it's dinosaur ghosts haunting oil-powered vehicles. A) we just got dinosaur ghosts in 4Kcon, B) the setup of this reminded me of one of the K-class scenarios in Doomcon.</p> <blockquote> <p>Exorcisms tailored for reptilian ectomorphs</p> </blockquote> <p>And I am just not into this.</p> <p>Novote on balance.</p> 
				 	]]>
