					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6739677#post-3894412</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6739677/scp-1750#post-3894412</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 01 Aug 2018 18:11:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>fieldstone</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1436137</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is great. What I love most about it - other than the sheer awesomeness of dinosaur ghosts possession as an idea - is that if I were new to SCP and coming across this as a first article, I would totally get this as a complete thing in itself, but it would also make me really want to know more about the Foundation and how it operates.</p> 
				 	]]>
